title: My 12 Books - November 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 12 books for this month 6 in PDFs & 6 in ePUB formats. Covers included in separate folder:

01. A Companion to Astronomy and Astrophysics
02. A Scientific Autobiography - S. Chandrasekhar
03. Archimedes to Hawking - Laws of Science and the Great Minds Behind Them
04. Basic Math & Pre-algebra For Dummies (2nd Ed)
05. Computers for Seniors For Dummies (4th Ed)
06. Gods and Goddesses in Greek Mythology
07. How to Swear Around the World
08. Outlook 2016 For Dummies
09. PowerPoint 2016 For Dummies
10. Simple Astronomy
11. Spatial Analysis - A Guide For Ecologists
12. Waking the Giant - How a changing climate triggers earthquakes, tsunamis, and volcanoes
